casebody.data:
Sharon THURBER, petitioner,
v.
AETNA LIFE INSURANCE COMPANY, et al. No. 13-130. Supreme Court of the United States June 9, 2014. Case below, 712 F.3d 654 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied. Justice BREYER took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
